From c6fc34628fcfa0de2c1149fa9cc23f62fc7b8b7e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude Code <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Apr 2026 08:07:16 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] Add Qt4 build system support

Add BUILD_WITH_QT4 option and conditional Qt4/Qt6 package detection.
Links to qjson4 library when Qt4 is enabled.

Changes:
- Add BUILD_WITH_QT4 option to root CMakeLists.txt
- Add Qt4 compatibility in all client CMakeLists files
- Replace Qt6::* with conditional Qt4/Qt6 components
- Link qjson4 library for Qt4 builds
- Lower macOS deployment target to 10.6 for Qt4
- Handle qt4_create_translation and qt4_add_resources
- Update qt_add_executable/qt_finalize_executable for Qt4

Modified: 8 CMakeLists.txt files (~200 lines)
